title: The Queen of Confidence Serena F*ing Kerrigan
description:
The Queen of Confidence, Serena F’ing Kerrigan is the on the pod, and she’s dishing on how we can all be bad-ass, confident bitches! The creator of the “Let’s F*cking Date” card games shares all the details surrounding her Instagram Live dating show during COVID, the inspiration for her legendary games, and how to live your best life! Plus, the inaugural “Give Them Lala Tour” has wrapped, and Lala has all the feels about her first time on the road, along with some news about potential future dates!
